# Internal engineering notes
CLAUDE.md
ARCHITECTURE.md

# Design source-of-truth (icons, SVGs, design tokens spec, handoff doc)
handoff/

# App-Store-specific entitlements file — public repo ships only the
# Direct distribution build. The sync_to_public.sh script also strips
# the Release-AppStore configuration and DEVELOPMENT_TEAM from the
# project file. This belt-and-suspenders rule ensures the entitlements
# never get committed even if a future sync ever drops them in by accident.
Dictly/Dictly/Dictly-AppStore.entitlements

# Local Claude/agent state
.claude/
.cursorrules

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Bundled Whisper models. The `base` variant (~139 MB) ships in-repo so
# the app works offline straight after clone. Larger variants (large-v3
# at ~547 MB etc.) are too big for plain git and must be fetched on
# demand with `python3 scripts/fetch_bundled_model.py <variant>`.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Dictly/BundledModels/*
!Dictly/BundledModels/openai_whisper-base/

